[30;1m67 | [0m[35m```python hl_lines="1 2"[0m

[30;1m70 | [0m[35m)[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m289[0m[34m of [0m[33m3090[0m[31m ]--[0m

   Pattern: [32m(npm owner|password|htpasswd|auth_?token|secret_?key|private_?key|authorized_keys?|npmrc|\.ssh|usersecrets?|api_?keys|nuget\.config|\.identityservice)[0m
[30;1m45 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m46 | [0m[35m!!! Warning[0m
[30;1m47 | [0m[35m    By default `create_schema` builds a schema with ALL model fields.[0m
[30;1m48 | [0m[35m    This can lead to accidental unwanted data exposure (like hashed password, in the above example).[0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35m    <br>[0m
[30;1m50 | [0m[35m    **Always** use `fields` or `exclude` arguments to explicitly define list of attributes.[0m

[30;1m156 | [0m[35m## Nested routers[0m
[30;1m157 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m158 | [0m[35mThere are also times when you need to split your logic up even more.[0m
[30;1m159 | [0m[35m**Django Ninja** makes it possible to include a router into another router as many times as you like[0m
[30;1m160 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m161 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m162 | [0m[35mBasically, what that means is that you have `add_router` both on the `api` instance and on the `rout[0m

[30;1m109 | [0m[35m## Request body + path + query parameters[0m
[30;1m110 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m111 | [0m[35mYou can also declare **body**, **path** and **query** parameters, all at the same time.[0m
[30;1m112 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m113 | [0m[35m**Django Ninja** will recognize each of them and take the data from the correct place.[0m
[30;1m114 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m99 | [0m[35m## Request body + path parameters[0m
[30;1m100 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m101 | [0m[35mYou can declare path parameters **and** body requests at the same time.[0m
[30;1m102 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m103 | [0m[35m**Django Ninja** will recognize that the function parameters that match path parameters should be **[0m
[30;1m104 | [0m[35m[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m2995[0m[34m of [0m[33m3090[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000610[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Linux[0m

[30;1m66 | [0m[35m* Read the body of the request as JSON.[0m
[30;1m67 | [0m[35m* Convert the corresponding types (if needed).[0m
[30;1m68 | [0m[35m* Validate the data.[0m
[30;1m69 | [0m[35m    * If the data is invalid, it will return a nice and meaningful error, indicating exactly where a[0m
[30;1m70 | [0m[35m* Give you the received data in the parameter `item`.[0m
[30;1m71 | [0m[35m    * Because you declared it in the function to be of type `Item`, you will also have all the edito[0m
[30;1m72 | [0m[35m      (completion, etc.) for all the attributes and their types.[0m
